# Ignore real project data — these stay on your Mac, never go to GitHub
projects/*/brief.md
projects/*/positioning.md
projects/*/screenshots/*.png
projects/*/screenshots/*.jpg
projects/*/screenshots/*.jpeg
projects/*/screenshots/*.gif
projects/*/screenshots/*.webp
projects/*/*.pptx
projects/*/*.docx
projects/*/*.pdf

# Keep the template (empty forms are fine to share)
!projects/_template/brief.md
!projects/_template/positioning.md
!projects/_template/screenshots/README.md

# Mac system files
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# Launches context files (contain internal roadmap info)
launches/*/context.md

# Product Knowledge Base — populated files stay LOCAL (contain unreleased
# features, pricing strategy, internal positioning). Only structure is shared.
context/*.md
!context/README.md
!context/_TEMPLATE.md
!context/design-system.md
